title: CHVRCHES Promo Instrumentals
description:
these are the instrumentals for Recover, Lies, Gun and The Mother We Share.

I wanted to have these tracks so I could play them in spotify so I've taken the 256K AAC files from youtube and converted them to 320kbps mp3. sadly i have no way of just taking the 256k AAC and putting it in a proper M4A container.

decided to upload them here so others might be able to listen to them outside of youtube without using a crappy youtube converter that has an output bit rate that's way to low. spectrogram on the youtube files is only 18.3khz so hopefully 320kbps mp3 won't hurt...

I can't find the original source on these but thanks to cadburykid141 on youtube for uploading them there.
